title: The Ultimate Fighter 14 - Team Bisping vs Team Miller
description:
The Ultimate Fighter: Team Bisping vs. Team Miller[2] is the fourteenth installment of the Ultimate Fighting Championship (UFC)-produced reality television series The Ultimate Fighter.

The UFC and Spike held open tryouts on March 21, 2011, in Newark, New Jersey. The casting call went out for Bantamweight and Featherweight fighters. All fighters that applied and tried out for the show must have had at least three professional fights and have been at least 21 years of age.
